    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with a visceral 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is in concours-level condition, boasting a pristine subframe and documented rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings for preventative longevity. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), the chassis remains composed under high-lateral loads while maintaining street-level compliance. No fluid weeping, zero deferred maintenance, and original paint depth verified across all panels. This is a blue-chip investment for the discerning purist seeking a mechanically flawless high-revving masterpiece.",
